title: Mr. Greg
description: Steven, Greg and Pearl take a trip to Empire City to live the good life.

title: The Curse
description: Craig, Kelsey and JP run afoul of some no-good teenage witches and are cursed! Lousy teenagers!

title: The Hard Easy
description: A delicate race of frog people employ Finn and Jake to help them deal with Prince Huge, an evil lizard creature who's ravaging the moss swamp.

title: What's Your Problem?
description: Amethyst convinces Steven to take a day off for himself.

title: Together Forever
description: Connie has a really clear vision for her future. Steven wants to make sure he'll be a part of it.

title: Jail Break
description: Steven teams up with a new ally to rescue the Gems.

title: Carmelita
description: Chata loans Xochi a car under the condition that Vic and Val can get rides when they need. However, the car becomes aggressive towards V&V and attacks!

title: I Am My Monster
description: Everything is not fine.

title: The Question
description: Steven shows some city slicker gems how the cowboys lived.

title: Escaramuza
description: When Val's favorite Escaramuza team loses a member, he convinces Xochi to join the squad. He becomes her coach and will do anything to win the big competition.

title: Princess Cookie
description: Finn and Jake are called on to solve a Candy Kingdom hostage crisis when a rogue cookie takes over.

title: Marcy & Hunson
description: Hunson Abadeer returns to Ooo to bond with his daughter Marceline, but will he be able to prove that he's changed his soul-sucking ways?

title: Fire & Ice
description: Kelsey and Stacks write a story for book club, which turns out to be more personal than Kelsey realized.

title: Sky Witch
description: Marceline is on a top-secret mission tracking Maja the Sky Witch. When she loses the witch's trail, Marceline turns to Princess Bubblegum for help.

title: Go With Me
description: Finn needs to date to the movies and must balance the contrasting advice of Jake and Marceline in wooing Princess Bubblegum so he can see that flick!

title: Band For Life
description: When Vic and Val tag along with Xochi to a punk concert, they want to prove that they're cool enough to hang out with her. But in a desperate attempt to be cool, they wind up destroying the concert.

title: Mindful Education
description: Steven and Connie need to learn greater focus to take their training to the next level.

title: Varmints
description: Bubblegum teams up with Marceline to face a threat to her homestead's citizens.

title: Now We're Only Falling Apart
description: Pearl tells a story.

title: What Was Missing
description: Finn and Jake do battle with a powerful door lord.

title: The Answer
description: Garnet finally tells Steven the story of how she came to be a Crystal Gem.

title: Prisoners of Love
description: The boys try to cool off but get trapped by the Ice King.

title: The Last Kid in the Creek
description: A terrible curse leaves Craig as the only kid in the creek.

title: Wheels
description: Kim Kil Whan is worried about his daughter's future and asks Jake for some parental advice.

title: Hit the Diamond
description: Steven and the Gems play an old fashioned game of baseball.

title: Los Cadejos
description: Val holds a grudge against Vic, unwittingly attracting an evil cadejo, a mythological wolf-like beast.

title: Alone Together
description: The Gems try to teach Steven to use his fusion powers.

title: Keystone Motel
description: Steven, Greg and Garnet go on a road trip.

title: Broke His Crown
description: When Ice King's magic crown goes haywire, Marceline and Princess Bubblegum resort to extreme measures to help him.
